Package: sys-scan
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight Linux security & hygiene scanner (process/network/module/IOC)
 A fast C++20 system scanner producing structured JSON findings with noise reduction,
 module integrity heuristics, and IOC aggregation. Includes optional process hashing
 and anomaly-only modes for cleaner CI gating.
